{"tha-ap272:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap272:0.2":"Padumukkhipavagga ","tha-ap272:0.3":"Taraniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap272:1.1":"“Suvannavanno sambuddho, ","tha-ap272:1.2":"vipassi dakkhinaraho; ","tha-ap272:1.3":"Naditire thito sattha, ","tha-ap272:1.4":"bhikkhusanghapurakkhato. ","tha-ap272:2.1":"Nava na vijjate tattha, ","tha-ap272:2.2":"santarani mahannave; ","tha-ap272:2.3":"Nadiya abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap272:2.4":"taresim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap272:3.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap272:3.2":"yam taresim naruttamam; ","tha-ap272:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap272:3.4":"taranaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap272:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap272:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap272:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap272:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma taraniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap272:6.1":"Taraniyattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap272:7.1":"Padumukkhipavaggo sattavisatimo. ","tha-ap272:8.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap272:9.1":"Ukkhipi telacandi ca, ","tha-ap272:9.2":"dipado ca bilalido; ","tha-ap272:9.3":"Maccho javo salalado, ","tha-ap272:9.4":"rakkhaso tarano dasa; ","tha-ap272:9.5":"Gathayo cettha sankhata, ","tha-ap272:9.6":"talisam cekameva cati. "}